Release: Telegram v1


    - WE needs to get by:
        +Telegram_Bot_Token
        +Telegram_Chat_ID

    ++ STEP How To Get Telegram Bot and Telegram Chat ID

    --> Get: Telegram Bot_Token from @BotFather
        * Start the bot:
            /start
            1. Create name the bot telegram (e.g., SuperBot)
            2. Take username your telegram bot, Make sure it must be end in `bot` (e.g., Superunixbot or Superunix_bot)
            3. It show will find at t.me/Superunixbot is username your telegram bot
            4. Is importan get token to access the HTTP API provide: (e.g., 845433:AFEFde@###) 
            
            **Note Your token secure and store it safely, it can be used by anyone to control your bot.
        IF problem you can contact @BotFather https://core.telegram.org/bots/api

    --> Get: Telegram Chat_ID from @userinfobot 
        /start
    e.g., 
        @username your telegram
        id: 834@###
        First: firstname
        Last: lastname
        Lang: en --> default english
        Registered: Check Date

        **Note you can use other optional cuz it have many tools control Menu:
        Such as: User, Bot, Group, Channel,...

**Read here workflow:

    - By default status payment (PEADING)

    - When user payment confrimed (Bakong responseCode 0),
    The API updates Order/Payment to (PAID) and sends a Telegram message.

    - When an orders expires (older than 5 minutes) and no Payments is not found,
    It marks (CANCLLED) and sends a telegram message
    
    - The background poller also sends duplicate alerts. 
    On fun (retryPayment), It's reset so a new notification can be sent for the attempt.

    




    